Pokémon Go announced that trainers will soon be able to hatch Togepi and Pichu and several other Pokémon that were originally discovered in the Johto Region. “These are the first of more Pokémon coming to Pokémon Go over the next few months,” said the game’s makers. The company added that from now until 29 December, players will also find limited edition Pikachu all over the world. “These Pikachu will be wearing a festive hat to celebrate the season.”